-- MOVES-John Levitske joins Houlihan Lokey as managing director
-- 
-- Tue Dec 16, 2014 02:48PM EST
-- None



Dec 16 (Reuters) - Investment bank Houlihan Lokey appointed John Levitske as a managing director to its dispute resolution and financial expert opinions practice.

Most recently, Levitske was a managing director at Duff & Phelps' dispute consulting division. He had earlier worked with Standard & Poor, KPMG [KPMG.UL]  and FTI Consulting Inc <FCN.N>.